              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Filter 134 keV. The filter components (g/cm2) were:",
                "58Ni-202., Cr-34.5, Si-121., 10B-0.2.",
                "Beam's purity given by authors in the article was 99%.",
                "Beam's purity calculated using ENF/B-8.0 library by the",
                "Filter.8 code is about 61%. Other additions to the",
                "main neutron line were about: a line with the energy",
                "46.8 keV - 21.4%, 54.0 keV - 2.3%, 84.6 keV - 7.4%,",
                "lines with energies above 135 keV less than 0.2%."
              ]
            }
          ],
